{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-308","title":"魔法与传说","sectionId":"chapter-14","sectionTitle":"人文历史需了解","pageStart":1500,"pageEnd":1504,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":23,"duplicateEntryCount":12,"pages":[{"number":1500,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"308 魔法与传说"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"witchcraft [ˈwɪtʃkrɑːft]","headword":"witchcraft"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巫术；魔法"},{"type":"entry","text":"wizard [ˈwɪzəd]","headword":"wizard"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巫师，男巫"},{"type":"entry","text":"witch [wɪtʃ]","headword":"witch"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.女巫"},{"type":"note","text":"◎witch doctor巫医"},{"type":"entry","text":"hag [hæɡ]","headword":"hag"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巫婆"},{"type":"entry","text":"sorcerer [ˈsɔːsərə(r)]","headword":"sorcerer"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.术士，男巫士"},{"type":"entry","text":"incant [ɪnˈkænt]","headword":"incant"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.念咒语"}]},{"number":1501,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"horoscope [ˈhɒrəskəʊp]","headword":"horoscope"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.占星术；星象"},{"type":"entry","text":"sacrifice [ˈsækrɪfaɪs]","headword":"sacrifice"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.祭品，供奉"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sacrifice to献祭/blood sacrifice血祭"},{"type":"entry","text":"wand [wɒnd]","headword":"wand"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.魔杖；棒"},{"type":"note","text":"◎magic wand魔杖"},{"type":"entry","text":"magical potion 神奇的药水","headword":"magical potion"},{"type":"entry","text":"crystal ball 水晶球","headword":"crystal ball"}]},{"number":1502,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"devil [ˈdevl]","headword":"devil"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.魔鬼"},{"type":"entry","text":"superstition [ˌsuːpəˈstɪʃn]","headword":"superstition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.迷信"},{"type":"note","text":"◎theological superstition神学迷信"},{"type":"entry","text":"superstitious [ˌsuːpəˈstɪʃəs]","headword":"superstitious"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.迷信的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎superstitious belief迷信，迷信观念"},{"type":"entry","text":"lost soul迷失的灵魂","headword":"lost soul"},{"type":"entry","text":"go to heaven 上天堂，归天，死","headword":"go to heaven"},{"type":"entry","text":"go to hell 下地狱","headword":"go to hell"},{"type":"entry","text":"black cat 黑猫","headword":"black cat"}]},{"number":1503,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"goblin [ˈɡɒblɪn]","headword":"goblin"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.妖精"},{"type":"entry","text":"zombie [ˈzɒmbi]","headword":"zombie"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.僵尸"},{"type":"entry","text":"vampire [ˈvæmpaɪə(r)]","headword":"vampire"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.吸血鬼"},{"type":"entry","text":"ghost [ɡəʊst]","headword":"ghost"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.鬼，幽灵"},{"type":"note","text":"◎lay a ghost驱除鬼魂"},{"type":"entry","text":"ghost story 鬼故事","headword":"ghost story"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"News about 4 and 14关于数字4和14的新闻"},{"type":"definition","text":"A new apartment building in Sydney, Australia, has mysteriously left"},{"type":"text","text":"off the numbers 4 and 14 from the elevator. The disappearance of the two"},{"type":"text","text":"floors is apparent because certain numbers are of bad luck or have"},{"type":"text","text":"associations with death among Chinese, who are investing billions of"},{"type":"text","text":"dollars in the Australian property market. In Mandarin Chinese, the sound"},{"type":"text","text":"of the word “four” is very similar to the word “death” and that could be bad"}]},{"number":1504,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"luck. This superstition is referred to as tetraphobia and is common in East"},{"type":"text","text":"Asian and Southeast Asian regions such as China, Japan, Malaysia and"},{"type":"text","text":"Korea."},{"type":"text","text":"在澳大利亚悉尼的一座新建的公寓楼内，电梯上的数"},{"type":"text","text":"字“4”和“14”神秘地消失了。这两个楼层数字消失的原因很明显，因为"},{"type":"text","text":"某些数字在中国人看来代表着噩运或者跟死亡有联系，而这些中国人"},{"type":"text","text":"正将几十亿美元的资金投入澳大利亚的房地产市场。在汉语普通话"},{"type":"text","text":"中，数字“4”和“死”发音很相似，代表着噩运。这种迷信行为被称"},{"type":"text","text":"为“恐四症”，在东亚和东南亚地区如中国、日本、韩国和马来西亚等"},{"type":"text","text":"国家很普遍。"}]}]}